rows.label: tlk4210018301_msg0002
rows.name:
Meh-meh! Lapupu engrossed in world
of fiction!

rows.label: tlk4210018301_msg0003
rows.name:
In fiction, Lapupu can become anyone!
Like swishy-swashy hero or fluffy-puff
princess or zip-a-zip fairy!

rows.label: tlk4210018301_msg0004
rows.name:
Becoming someone else make it easier
to understand others, show kindness.
Lapupu want everyone to realize this.
